    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic balance of performance and reliability, perfect for a buyer seeking a well-maintained daily driver. The exterior is finished in a sophisticated Metallic Graphite that retains a brilliant shine; while there are a few minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small, superficial scratch near the rear wheel well, the body remains straight and free of any dents. Inside, the smoke-free cabin is in excellent shape, featuring charcoal leather seats with only light creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Every electronic component, from the premium audio system to the heated seats and navigation, functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is sound and has been serviced regularly at 5,000-mile intervals. We recently completed a full synthetic oil change and a multi-point inspection, confirming the brakes have 60% life remaining and the tires are in great health. The engine runs quietly, the transmission shifts are crisp, and there are absolutely no dashboard warning lights. Included with the sale are two sets of keys, the original owner\u2019s manuals, and a detailed folder of service receipts to provide total peace of mind.",
